originalText.text:
Everyone is truly wonderful, supportive, and so thoroughly professional.  I have had the recent fortune to connect with one of the best optical surgeons that totally relieved all of my anxieties -- Dr. Nataneli ( pulling from memory the very next day after my procedure -- hoping I am correct in spelling!)
A special acknowledgement to Elisa who took wonderful care of me at both the Bronx and East Harlem locations.  And also a special shout-out to Dr. Former, who did my culminating follow-up exam, himself, as he made me laugh in regard to my red-sequinned boots, which he stated made him feel like he was in the Wizard of Oz with the ruby slippers!
